This sticker can be applied to any weapon you own and can be scraped to look more worn. You can scrape the same sticker multiple times, making it a bit more worn each time, until it is removed from the weapon.
Exterior: Battle-Scarred
Versatile but expensive, the German-made MP7 SMG is the perfect choice for high-impact close-range combat. It has been spray-painted with a blue pattern over a yellow base. Your personal battle cry
The Spectrum Collection
Exterior: Well-Worn

An ideal pistol for the Terrorist on the move, the Tec-9 is lethal in close quarters and features a high magazine capacity. It has been custom painted to resemble a flashbang grenade. Re: Dance lessons with Jordan
The CS20 Collection
Exterior: Field-Tested
This item features StatTrak™ technology, which tracks certain statistics when equipped by its owner.
This item tracks Confirmed Kills.

The classic Sawed-Off deals very heavy close-range damage, but with its low accuracy, high spread and slow rate of fire, you'd better kill what you hit. It has been custom painted to resemble a heavily played spirit board. "Come on, I know you're moving it..."
The Dreams & Nightmares Collection
Exterior: Field-Tested

The CT-exclusive Mag-7 delivers a devastating amount of damage at close range. Its rapid magazine-style reloads make it a great tactical choice. It has been painted using a combination of subtly patterned hydrographics and dry-transfer decals of wings. Sometimes the wings of an angel don't mean salvation
The Phoenix Collection
Exterior: Battle-Scarred
This item features StatTrak™ technology, which tracks certain statistics when equipped by its owner.

Essentially a box that bullets come out of, the MAC-10 SMG boasts a high rate of fire, with poor spread accuracy and high recoil as trade-offs. Red, tan, and green monkeys adorn this custom painted MAC-10. Spunky monkeys!
The Recoil Collection
Exterior: Minimal Wear

The classic Sawed-Off deals very heavy close-range damage, but with its low accuracy, high spread and slow rate of fire, you'd better kill what you hit. It has been given a skull hydrographic and hand painted gold accents. Rosencrantz and Guildenstern never had a chance...
The Revolver Case Collection
Exterior: Well-Worn

The pricy G3SG1 lowers movement speed considerably but compensates with a higher rate of fire than other sniper rifles. It has been custom painted using Danger Zone's tactical map display as inspiration. You have all the information you need - Franz Kriegeld, Phoenix Tactician
